---
// Icon SVG sudah disesuaikan untuk masing-masing layanan
---

<section id="services" class="py-24 bg-[#F8F9FA]">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    
    <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <span class="text-[#7E67F8] font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-sm mb-4 block font-mulish">
        Layanan Unggulan
      </span>
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 font-oswald uppercase leading-tight">
        Solusi Digital <span class="text-[#7E67F8]">Terpadu</span> Untuk Bisnis Anda.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-slate-500 font-mulish text-sm md:text-base">
        Kami menyediakan solusi pembuatan website dan konten strategis yang dirancang khusus untuk meningkatkan performa bisnis Anda di dunia digital.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
      
      <div class="group bg-white p-8 rounded-sm shadow-sm border-b-4 border-transparent hover:border-[#7E67F8] hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 transform hover:-translate-y-2">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-[#7E67F8]/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-[#7E67F8] transition-colors duration-500">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-7 w-7 text-[#7E67F8] group-hover:text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 font-oswald uppercase leading-tight">Landing Page</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-500 mb-6 font-mulish text-xs leading-relaxed">
          Halaman penjualan yang didesain khusus untuk konversi tinggi. Cocok untuk kampanye iklan FB/IG Ads.
        </p>
        <a href="#" class="text-[#7E67F8] font-bold text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest font-oswald group-hover:text-slate-900 transition-colors">Read More +</a>
      </div>

      <div class="group bg-white p-8 rounded-sm shadow-sm border-b-4 border-transparent hover:border-[#7E67F8] hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 transform hover:-translate-y-2">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-[#7E67F8]/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-[#7E67F8] transition-colors duration-500">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-7 w-7 text-[#7E67F8] group-hover:text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M16 11V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4M5 9h14l1 12H4L5 9z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 font-oswald uppercase leading-tight">Website UMKM</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-500 mb-6 font-mulish text-xs leading-relaxed">
          Paket website ekonomis dengan fitur lengkap. Solusi tepat bagi UMKM yang ingin mulai go-digital.
        </p>
        <a href="#" class="text-[#7E67F8] font-bold text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest font-oswald group-hover:text-slate-900 transition-colors">Read More +</a>
      </div>

      <div class="group bg-white p-8 rounded-sm shadow-sm border-b-4 border-transparent hover:border-[#7E67F8] hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 transform hover:-translate-y-2">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-[#7E67F8]/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-[#7E67F8] transition-colors duration-500">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-7 w-7 text-[#7E67F8] group-hover:text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 font-oswald uppercase leading-tight">Company Profile</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-500 mb-6 font-mulish text-xs leading-relaxed">
          Tampil profesional di mata klien. Website profil perusahaan dengan desain premium dan elegan.
        </p>
        <a href="#" class="text-[#7E67F8] font-bold text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest font-oswald group-hover:text-slate-900 transition-colors">Read More +</a>
      </div>

      <div class="group bg-white p-8 rounded-sm shadow-sm border-b-4 border-transparent hover:border-[#7E67F8] hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 transform hover:-translate-y-2">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-[#7E67F8]/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-[#7E67F8] transition-colors duration-500">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-7 w-7 text-[#7E67F8] group-hover:text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M11 5H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v11a2 2 0 002 2h11a2 2 0 002-2v-5m-1.414-9.414a2 2 0 112.828 2.828L11.828 15H9v-2.828l8.586-8.586z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 font-oswald uppercase leading-tight">Jasa Artikel SEO</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-500 mb-6 font-mulish text-xs leading-relaxed">
          Optimasi konten agar website muncul di Google. Artikel berkualitas untuk menarik trafik potensial.
        </p>
        <a href="#" class="text-[#7E67F8] font-bold text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest font-oswald group-hover:text-slate-900 transition-colors">Read More +</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>